newsitem.title: UK: NWE jet fuel strong, availability tight.
newsitem.headline: NWE jet fuel strong, availability tight.

text.p: NWE jet was firm on Friday as benchmark futures retained recent gains and availability both in the north and the Mediterranean remained tight, traders said.
On the cif cargo market, premiums were put Sept IPE +$33/+$34. Barges were put at Sept IPE +$21/+$22, fob ARA.

In the Mediterranean, the situation remained tight with Middle Eastern demand gobbling up supply. A Libyan cargo was traded fob Med +$8.0 on Thursday and traders the next Libyan done could fetch as much as fob Med +$11.0. -- London Newsroom, +44 171 542 7714.3
